The Stark & Wayne KAFKA™ for PCF brings Apache KAFKA™ to the Pivotal Cloud Foundry Platform. Apache KAFKA™ is used for building real-time data pipelines and streaming apps. It is horizontally scalable, fault-tolerant, wicked fast, and runs in production in thousands of companies.

The Stark & Wayne KAFKA™ tile brings KAFKA to everyone in your organization. New staff on their first day will find it simple to get started. Each service instance is a Kafka topic to which an application can subscribe or publish.

## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

Stark & Wayne Kafka is the most approachable way to leverage Apache Kafka™ on PCF. Easily provision your infrastructure to provide Kafka to your developers. The tile includes zookeeper to manage the health of Kafka. The tile also includes a spark integration. 

Take a look at the Kafka [use cases](https://kafka.apache.org/uses) to figure out how you can extend your app. 

## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

Stark & Wayne KAFKA™ for PCF includes the following key features:

* Topic per Service
* Spark Integration
* Zookeeper for high availablity

